  <h2>Example autocomplete</h2>

  <p>Using the typeahead.js plugin, we built a simple autocomplete widget:</p>


  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete" type="text"></input>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete").richAutocomplete({ source: source });
    </script>
  </p>

  <p>Using autocomplete with function as a source:</p>

  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete-function" type="text"></input>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete-function").richAutocomplete({ source: function (request, response) {
        response($.ui.autocomplete.filter(source, request.term));
      }
      });
    </script>
  </p>


  <p>Simulating request delay:</p>

  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete-delay" type="text"></input>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete-delay").richAutocomplete({ source: function (request, response) {
        setTimeout(function () {
          response($.ui.autocomplete.filter(source, request.term));
        }, 500);
      }
      });
    </script>
  </p>

  <p>Simulating request delay with cached ajax mode:</p>

  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete-cache-delay" type="text"/>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete-cache-delay").richAutocomplete({
        cached: true,
        minLength: 2,
        source: function (request, response) {
          setTimeout(function () {
            response($.ui.autocomplete.filter(source, request.term));
          }, 500);
        }
      });
    </script>
  </p>

  <p>Auto-Focus:</p>

  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete-auto-focus" type="text"></input>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete-auto-focus").richAutocomplete({ source: source, autoFocus: true });
    </script>
  </p>



  <p>Auto-Fill:</p>

  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete-auto-fill" type="text"></input>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete-auto-fill").richAutocomplete({ source: source, autoFill: true });
    </script>
  </p>



  <p>Auto-Focus Auto-Fill:</p>

  <p>
    <input id="autocomplete-auto-focus-fill" type="text"></input>
    <script>
      $("#autocomplete-auto-focus-fill").richAutocomplete({ source: source, autoFocus: true, autoFill: true });
